cu.explanation_en: Setting the ciphering algorithm to the unknown enum 'nea9' will cause negotiation failure during the security setup phase.

du.explanation_en: Setting the PHY log level to an unknown enum 'invalid' will result in logging configuration errors and potential runtime issues.
du.explanation_zh: 將 PHY 日誌級別設定為未知的枚舉值 'invalid' 會導致日誌配置錯誤，並可能造成運行時問題。
